ActPilotage Act
PrecisApproval of the appointment by the Minister of Transport of GINETTE IDA MARIE BRINDLE of Essex, Ontario, to be a member of the Great Lakes Pilotage Authority, to hold office during pleasure for a term of four years, effective January 15, 2019, in the place of Michel Desrochers, whose term has expired.
